		isunique="yes"
		description="An exorcist can sense negative energy directed toward a person and disperse that energy to defeat curses and evil spells. To perform this technique, the exorcist must be in the presence of the person suffering from the curse. Facing that person and meditating for an hour, he performs a Test of Earth + Exorcism with an ST determined by the power of the spell to be defeated, often the result of the Test required to create the curse. Where the exorcist succeeds the curse is immediately lifted, but where he fails, he too suffers the effects of the curse for a number of weeks equal to the difference between his Test result and the ST.">
